                  >
                    We have updated the description engine to prioritize
                    readability and conversion.
                  </p>

                  <!-- SECTION 1 -->
                  <h2
                    style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 17px; color: #111111; font-weight: 600;"
                  >
                    1. Structured Bullet Points
                  </h2>
                  <p
                    style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555555;"
                  >
                    To help buyers scan your items faster, the AI now organizes
                    key product details (Size, Brand, Condition) into clean
                    bullet points by default.
                  </p>

                  <!-- IMAGE 1: Wide snippet -->
                  <div
                    style="margin-bottom: 35px; border: 1px solid #eaeaea; border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden;"
                  >
                    <img
                      src="https://autolister.app/update-133.png"
                      alt="New structured description format"
                      width="520"
                      style="display: block; width: 100%; max-width: 100%; height: auto; background-color: #f9f9f9;"
                      class="fluid-img"
                    />
                  </div>

                  <!-- SECTION 2 -->
                  <h2
                    style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 17px; color: #111111; font-weight: 600;"
                  >
                    2. Formatting Preferences
                  </h2>
                  <p
                    style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #555555;"
                  >
                    You retain full control over your listing style. A new <strong
