                          upload multiple items via mobile and generate all
                          descriptions simultaneously.
                        </p>

                        <!-- IMAGE 3: Teaser Image -->
                        <div
                          style="border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); background-color: #ffffff;"
